Package dsa.impl

Class BinarySearchTreeMap<K extends Comparable<K>,V>

java.lang.Object
dsa.impl.AbstractBinaryTree<IEntry<K,V>>
dsa.impl.ProperLinkedBinaryTree<IEntry<K,V>>
dsa.impl.BinarySearchTreeMap<K,V>
Type Parameters:
K - Generic type of the keys to be stored in the Map. All iterator methods should iterate in key order.
V - Generic type of the values to be stored in the Map.
All Implemented Interfaces:
IBinaryTree<IEntry<K,V>>, IMap<K,V>, ISortedMap<K,V>, ITree<IEntry<K,V>>
public class BinarySearchTreeMap<K extends Comparable<K>,V> extends ProperLinkedBinaryTree<IEntry<K,V>> implements ISortedMap<K,V>
Implementation of the Sorted Map ADT using a Binary Search Tree as the implementing data structure.
